<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Tiny Framework</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background: #fff;
        }
        #content {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="content">
    <h1>Welcome to Tiny Framework!</h1>
    <div>
        <p>You have successfully installed Tiny Framework. What's next?</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Enter your database credentials in <em>config/settings.php</em></li>
            <li>Setup your routes in <em>config/routes.php</em></li>
            <li>Create your modules in <em>modules/</em> directory</li>
            <li>Test if <a href="{url route='test'}">routes are working</a>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Happy coding!</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>